{
  "texts": [
    "Each story was scored according to scoring guidelines from the ESI studies of Madore et al. (2014) and Jing et al. (2016), which were adapted from the standard interview scoring (Levine et al., 2002).",
    "In their scoring, van Genugten et al.",
    "also considered all event details as internal details.",
    "This procedure differs from previous guidelines, which only considered details from the central events to be internal.",
    "This change was made to ensure that no episodic details were marked as external."
  ]
}